column16: Russell Branyan singles on a fly ball to right fielder Gary Matthews.    Ken Griffey scores.    Adrian Beltre to 2nd.
Russell Branyan doubles (2) on a ground ball to right fielder Gary Matthews.    Endy Chavez scores.    Adrian Beltre to 3rd.
Daniel Davidson intentionally walks Adrian Beltre.
Ken Griffey pops out to second baseman Howard Kendrick.
Endy Chavez singles on a fly ball to center fielder Torii Hunter.
Ichiro Suzuki lines out to shortstop Erick Aybar.
Curtis Granderson walks.    Josh Anderson scores.    Jeff Larish to 3rd.    Adam Everett to 2nd.
Brendan Harris flies out to center fielder Torii Hunter.
Jason Kubel lines out to right fielder Robb Quinlan.
Justin Morneau grounds out, second baseman Howard Kendrick to first baseman Kendry Morales.
